            <div>
                <h2>Frenchie/Rue du Nil </h2>
                <h4>5 Rue du Nil, 75002</h4>
                <p>We are setting up an association with all of the merchants on our street, Rue du Nil, where Frenchie is located. We all share the same philosophy: eat and sell quality products sourced from responsible suppliers. We plan to organize block parties, decorate the street at Christmas, and perhaps less glamorous- collective garbage pick up.</p>
