                {{/if}}
            </div>
            <div>
                <h2>Direction Trouville</h2>
                <p>Sometimes, on Sundays,  we run away from Paris with the kids, go to see the ocean, eat at Les Vapeurs, and then head back home relaxed and revived.</p>
            </div>
